ZH: 这支笔是我的。
EN: This pen is mine.

ZH: 请借我一支笔。
EN: Can you lend me a pen, please?

ZH: 我的笔没墨了。
EN: My pen is out of ink.

ZH: 他用钢笔写字。
EN: He writes with a fountain pen.

ZH: 我的毛笔是一种很老的款式。
EN: My brush pen is a very old style.

ZH: 我不喜欢写毛笔字。
EN: I don't like writing calligraphy with a brush pen.

ZH: 这支型号的钢笔很好用。
EN: This model of fountain pen is very easy to use.

ZH: 我的毛笔书法不太好。
EN: My calligraphy with a brush pen is not very good.

ZH: 我用这支笔写下了我的名字。
EN: I wrote my name with this pen.

ZH: 这支红笔不见了。
EN: This red pen is missing.

ZH: 他买了一套画笔。
EN: He bought a set of paintbrushes.

ZH: 请给我一支铅笔。
EN: Please give me a pencil.

ZH: 她在画画时最喜欢用马克笔。
EN: She prefers using markers when drawing.

ZH: 我给你准备了一支新的圆珠笔。
EN: I have prepared a new ballpoint pen for you.

ZH: 他的书包里装满了各种笔。
EN: His backpack is full of different types of pens.

ZH: 在考试时只能用黑色墨水的笔。
EN: Only black ink pens are allowed during the exam.

ZH: 我已经购买了一支签字笔。
EN: I have purchased a signature pen.

ZH: 这支钢笔可以擦除错误。
EN: This fountain pen can erase mistakes.

ZH: 我们在艺术课上使用各种各样的笔。
EN: We use all kinds of pens in art class.

ZH: 这只笔已经使用了很长时间。
EN: This pen has been used for a long time.
